<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>진료 완료 내역</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/tailwind.min.css">
    <script src="/js/lucide.min.js"></script>
</head>
<body class="bg-slate-50 p-6">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-100 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-green-600">
                <i data-lucide="check-circle" class="w-6 h-6"></i>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-800">진료 완료 내역</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 mt-1">오늘 진료가 완료된 환자 목록입니다.</p>
            </div>
            
            <form action="/doctor/completed-list" method="GET" class="relative w-full md:w-64 ml-auto">
                <i data-lucide="search" class="absolute left-3 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-4 h-4 text-slate-400"></i>
                <input
                    type="text"
                    name="keyword"
                    value=""
                    placeholder="환자명 검색..."
                    class="w-full pl-10 pr-4 py-2 border border-slate-200 rounded-lg focus:ring-2 focus:ring-green-500 outline-none text-sm"
                />
            </form>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
            <div class="col-span-full text-center py-10 text-slate-500">완료된 진료 내역이 없습니다.</div>
        </div>

        <nav class="flex gap-2 mt-6 justify-center"><span class="px-3 py-1 bg-indigo-600 text-white rounded">1</span></nav>
    </div>

    <script>
        lucide.createIcons();
    </script>
</body>
</html>